title: Microsoft Azure Virtual Network Gateways: Remote Peering
agents: azure_v2
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors remote peerings of a Microsoft Azure
 virtual network gateway.
 The state is WARN if the remote peering's sync level isn't
 "FullyInSync" or state isn't "Connected".

 In order to use this check, you need to configure the Azure special agent.

discovery:
 One service is created for each remote peering.
